<TITLE>
The Underwater Panther (Great Water Lynx, Night Panther, Mishibizhiw)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Underwater Panther,
Great Water Lynx, or Night Panther, a lake monster of the Algonquian tribes.">
