http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0803275781/natilangofthe-20
">Ojibway Tales</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Good collection of traditional folktales retold by an Ojibway author.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0803293380/natilangofthe-20
">Algonquian Spirit</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Excellent anthology of stories, songs, and oral history from the Ojibwe and other Algonquian tribes.
